== The Energy Chain: Ten Steps from Substrate to ATP


Cellular ATP production proceeds in a chain of functionally dependent steps. Each step is necessary but not sufficient on its own, and failure at any one step can propagate to downstream capacity loss. This chapter organizes the chain into ten steps and reviews each step's normal function, ATP accounting, documented ME/CFS findings, documented failure modes, and research gaps.

